himL.head: Bauvorankündigung
himL.text: Bauvorankündigung: Vom 06.01. - 27.01.2025 verkehren die Züge der Linie RE8 aufgrund von Bauarbeiten der DB InfraGO AG nur von/bis Berlin Friedrichstraße. Die Halte Flughafen BER, Berlin Ostkreuz, Berlin Ostbahnhof und Berlin Alexanderplatz entfallen. Bitte weichen Sie auf alternative Verbindungen aus.

himL.head: Attention: Construction work with journey cancellations for RE1, RE2, RE7, RE8, RB23
himL.text: Due to construction work on the railway line in Berlin, regional trains in Berlin are running differently. RE1 does not run between Erkner and Ostkreuz, RE2 does not run between Friedrichstraße and Königs Wusterhausen, RE7 does not run between Berlin Zoo and Königs Wusterhausen (repeaters do not run Wannsee - Lübbenau - Cottbus), RE8 does not run between Friedrichstraße and BER Airport and RB23 does not run at all. The construction timetables are included in the timetable information.
